
---

# 5. `.gitignore`

Paste this into `.gitignore`:

```gitignore
# Environment variables
.env
.env.local

# Virtual environments
venv/
.venv/
env/
ENV/

# Python cache and build artifacts
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.so
.Python
build/
dist/
downloads/
eggs/
.eggs/
lib/
lib64/
parts/
sdist/
var/
wheels/
*.egg-info/
.installed.cfg
*.egg

# IDE and editor files
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# Operating system files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Jupyter
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# Large files and datasets
data/
*.zip

# Testing and coverage
.pytest_cache/
.coverage

# Logs
*.log
logs/